I already liked you guys I mean Diljit and Gurdaas G, but after this song I respect you guys more..See guys? This is how we are.. We don't need to hate each other I mean India and Pakistan, I know religion is different but still guys we are the same no? Spread love guys not hatred! 
1. Ravi to Chenaab pochda ki haaal hai sutluj da? (Ah loved it)
2. Sanu sauda nai pugda ( yaar I will say the same, sauda raaas nai aya )
3. Waghay day border tay raah pochdi lahoraaan day ( I wish I could remove all the barriers and put all of us together, no? )
4. Most favourite line ( ALLAH bismillah teri jugni, Saaiyan borhan waliye way jugni )
Love & respect from Pak-Canada❤️🤙🏻
